x4freetext: -FAST NEUTRON SCATTERING FROM LA-139, PR-141, ER,
5.5 MV VAN DE GRAAFF ACCELERATOR AND
ABOVE 2 MEV AND 60 KEV BELOW THIS ENERGY.
X 4 INCH) MOUNTED ON AN XP-1040 PHOTOMULTI-
PLIER WITH A NEUTRON-GAMMA RAY PULSE-SHAPE
.ABOUT 10 CM FROM THE CENTRE OF THE GASS-CELL TO THE
SCATTERER, AND 4.0 METER FROM THE SCATTERER TO THE
A.P.T. JAPAN CODE CHANGED TO JPN
.MULTIPLE SCATTERING AND ATTENUATION OF NEUTRON FLUX
IN THE SAMPLE, AND SOURCE-TO-SAMPLE GEOMETRICAL
.ERRORS INDICATED CONTAIN STATISTICAL ERRORS AND ERRORS
ORIGINATING IN THE PEELING-OFF PROCESS WHEN IT IS
.A PEELING-OFF METHOD WAS APPLIED TO UNRESOLVED PEAKS
